\
Validation expectations\
- Every input measure_id must appear once.\
- If label = multi_measure_rest, rest_count must be an integer >= 2.\
- If label != multi_measure_rest, rest_count must be null.\
- If many measures are hard to classify safely, include a low_confidence_page warning.\
- If uncertain, do not guess.\
\
END OF PROMPT\
\
